WEBVTT

00:00:28.290 --> 00:00:31.310
yaratish muammoga yechim bo'lsa-chi?

00:00:31.310 --> 00:00:32.770
G'oya g'alati tuyulishi
mumkin,

00:00:32.770 --> 00:00:33.920
ammo unday emas.

00:00:33.920 --> 00:00:35.763
Avvaliga beton yaratish jarayonini

00:00:35.763 --> 00:00:37.453
o'rganish va uni o'z maqsadimizga

00:00:37.453 --> 00:00:39.243
qanday bo'ysundirishni

00:00:39.243 --> 00:00:40.633
bilish lozim.

00:00:40.648 --> 00:00:42.798
Beton shag'al va qum aralashmasidan

00:00:42.798 --> 00:00:45.146
iborat agregatlarni loy va ohaktoshning

00:00:45.146 --> 00:00:47.576
kukunli aralashmasi bo'lgan sementga

00:00:47.576 --> 00:00:49.236
qorishtirish orqali tayyorlanadi.

00:00:49.245 --> 00:00:51.185
Qorishmaga suv qo'shilgach,

00:00:51.185 --> 00:00:52.815
sement quyuqlashib,
agregatlar

00:00:52.815 --> 00:00:55.045
bilan qoplanadi va 
gidratatsiya deb ataluvchi

00:00:55.045 --> 00:00:56.275
kimyoviy reaksiya tufayli

00:00:56.275 --> 00:00:58.075
tezda qotib qoladi.

00:00:58.077 --> 00:00:59.937
Natijada, yuzlab metr balandlikka

00:00:59.937 --> 00:01:02.247
ko'tariluvchi binolarni qurish uchun